2005-10-26 13:19  ehofman

	* simgear/threads/SGThread.hxx: Back out the shared mutex code
	  since it only works when the mutex is in shared memory[1],
	  something we don't support anyhow.  This also fixes a FreeBSD
	  compile problem.

